---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Sync by PulseLab" description="Sync Privacy Policy. Your cycle data stays on your device. We never collect, store, or share your personal information.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-8 px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/sync" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[var(--primary)] mb-6 hover:underline">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        Back to Sync
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--text-dark)] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-[var(--primary)]">Sync by PulseLab</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-8 px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="highlight-box mb-10">
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--text-dark)]">
          <strong>The short version:</strong> Sync stores all your data locally on your device. We never collect, transmit, or have access to your personal cycle information. Period.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Our Privacy Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          We built Sync with a simple principle: your cycle data is deeply personal and should never leave your device. We designed the app so that we literally cannot access your data - it's not stored on our servers because we don't have servers that store user data.
        </p>

        <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
        <div class="data-table">
          <div class="data-row">
            <div class="data-label">Personal Information</div>
            <div class="data-value"><span class="badge">None</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="data-row">
            <div class="data-label">Cycle Data</div>
            <div class="data-value"><span class="badge">None</span> - stored on device only</div>
          </div>
          <div class="data-row">
            <div class="data-label">Usage Analytics</div>
            <div class="data-value"><span class="badge">None</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="data-row">
            <div class="data-label">Advertising Data</div>
            <div class="data-value"><span class="badge">None</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="data-row">
            <div class="data-label">Account Information</div>
            <div class="data-value"><span class="badge">None</span> - no account required</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Data Stored on Your Device</h2>
        <p>Sync stores the following data locally on your iPhone:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Period start and end dates</li>
          <li>Cycle predictions and fertile window calculations</li>
          <li>Any notes you add to calendar entries</li>
          <li>Your app preferences and settings</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This data never leaves your device. There is no cloud sync, no backup to our servers, and no way for us to access it.</p>

        <h2>No Internet Required</h2>
        <p>Sync works completely offline. The app never connects to the internet for any reason related to your personal data. You can use Sync in airplane mode indefinitely.</p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Sync does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services. The app does not contain any SDKs that collect user data.</p>

        <h2>Data Deletion</h2>
        <p>Since all data is stored locally on your device, you have complete control. To delete your data:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Delete individual entries within the app</li>
          <li>Use the reset option in Settings</li>
          <li>Delete the app from your device</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Once deleted, data cannot be recovered because we don't have any backup of your information.</p>

        <h2>Why This Matters</h2>
        <p>In recent years, concerns have grown about how period tracking apps handle sensitive health data. Some apps have been found sharing data with advertisers, law enforcement, or other third parties. We believe this is unacceptable.</p>
        <p>By keeping everything on your device, we've eliminated these risks entirely. We can't share what we don't have.</p>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Sync is not intended for use by children under 13. We do not knowingly collect any information from children.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>If we make changes to this privacy policy, we will update this page and note the date of the last revision below. Our commitment to not collecting your data will not change.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or Sync's privacy practices, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:hello@pulselab.cc">hello@pulselab.cc</a></p>

        <div class="last-updated">
          Last updated: January 2026
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .highlight-box {
    background: white;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .prose {
    color: var(--text-medium);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .prose ul {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .prose a:hover {
    color: var(--primary-dark);
  }

  .data-table {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .data-row {
    display: flex;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 180, 160, 0.1);
  }

  .data-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .data-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    width: 200px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .data-value {
    color: var(--text-medium);
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 180, 160, 0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .data-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .data-label {
      width: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
